<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Essential Chart supports the <Bold>Bubble Chart </Bold> type. In this demo, series displayed in Bubble chart type with its data labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Segments can be shown with different interior colors by enabling the <Bold>ColorEach</Bold> property of ChartSeries.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> helps to apply palette for ChartArea.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Template Options"</Bold> helps to choose the template for the Bubble Chart </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"ShowDataLabels"</Bold> sets the visibility of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"HorizontalAlignment"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels horizontally. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"VerticalAlignment"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels vertically. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>

